noctalia-v5-git (5.0.0+git20260527.0000000-1) ceres; urgency=medium

  * Initial Devuan-Nexus build of Noctalia v5 alpha.
  * Full C++ rewrite using cairo/pango rendering — no Qt6 dependency.
  * Built without systemd; uses elogind's sd-bus via sdbus-c++.
  * Optimized for x86-64-v3 with -O3.

